      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWEET CONFETTI (1) produced a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 411m behind Heroic Federer (23.92) in a Grade 4. Was a winner prior to that. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Key runner on her best form. DRILL BABY (4) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in six starts, including three wins and three placings. Recorded a 2 length win (27.94) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. REMI NATH (6) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Country Form (23.64) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Has good speed so she should be prominent despite the draw. Can feature again. CHARLI'S BEGONIA (2) is another with top-three prospects.",
